<DATE1>  27 Jan 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> HONG KONG &amp; MACAO </F>
<F P=101> Hong Kong </F>
<H3> <TI>   Li Tieying Meets Visitors From Hong Kong </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW2701043294 Beijing XINHUA in English 0353 GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2701043294 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, January 27 (XINHUA) -- Li Tieying, state 
councillor and minister in charge of the State Commission for 
Restructuring the Economy, met with Sir Jack Cater, chairman of 
H.G. Asia Ltd, a Hong Kong-based securities firm, and his party 
here this morning. 
  Sir Cater and his party arrived here yesterday as guests of 
the commission. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-46260 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drchi018_w_94012" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-CHI-94-018 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  27 Jan 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> HONG KONG &amp; MACAO </F>
<F P=101> Hong Kong </F>
