<TEXT>
Article   Type:BFN 

  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese at 1138 GMT on 
24 January carries a 737-character report on Chinese 
Vice-Premier and Foreign Minister Qian Qichen meeting French 
Prime Minister Edouard Balladur in Paris on 24 January. 
  The XINHUA Domestic version has been compared to the XINHUA 
English item published in the 25 January China Daily report on 
page 21 and contains the following variations: 
